snippet.title: COLLECTION of SaGa FINAL FANTASY LEGEND - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The first three titles in the SaGa series come to #NintendoSwitch in one collection! Battle through fantasy worlds across these classic Game Boy titles when #CollectionofSaGa #FinalFantasy Legend launches on 12/15.

https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/collection-of-saga-final-fantasy-legend-switch/

#CollectionofSaGa #NintendoSwitch
